name: Your Turn
description:
Nothing is as classic to me like watching the locals play chess in a New York City park. The old fogeys used to collect here and play all day, and we had no idea what was going on. Striking to see one of the oldest board games on the planet sitting and waiting for new players to arrive.

3240x2160 JPEG

Photo by Jason Charnick
Taken in the Bronx, NY, USA
